# Rule: Strict schema for sidecar metadata

- Sidecar files MUST conform to os_meta/schema.yaml exactly.
- No extra keys allowed.
- Enum values MUST come from os_meta/vocab.yaml.
- Entity IDs MUST come from os_meta/entity_registry.yaml.

If you detect an unknown vocab/entity, do NOT guess:
- Add comp_conflicts: ["conflict:unknown_vocab"] or ["conflict:unknown_entity"]
- Set comp_safety_mode: locked_down
- Set comp_label_quality: auto_low
